    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly with plenty of power, and the transmission shifts seamlessly, ensuring a reliable and comfortable driving experience. While there are a few minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with its age, the interior remains clean and the overall mechanical integrity is excellent. It is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a high-quality, pre-owned vehicle.",
